<p><strong>只显示迭代段落页：</strong>以方便用来检查这些页面的状态。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:author-page-tool&#32;category=fragment]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>只展示原创SCP：</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:author-page-tool&#32;tag=+原创&#32;+SCP]]</span></p>
